R Markdown

This R Markdown document is part of SMUs Masters in Data Science Program DS 6306 Doing Data Science. Students are given a data set and asked to make predictions using data science methods and techniques learned in the course. For this case study we are asumming that we have been hired by a company called DDSAnalytics that specializes in talent management. The company wants to gain a competitive edge by providing its customers with accurate predictions regarding attrition (employee turnover) and monthly salary.

We will start by importing the following data for analysis:

CaseStudy2-Data.csv:

  1. Later we will import the folowing data sets that will used to make our predictions for the class contest.
  • CaseStudy2CompSet No Attritioin.csv
  • CaseStudy2CompSet No Solary.csv
